### Create competition
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/competitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name":      "TEST FISA et Championnat du Maroc d'Hiver",
  "type":      "test_fisa",
  "location":  "Salle Ahmed Chehoud",
  "city":      "Casablanca",
  "startDate": "2026-04-11",
  "endDate":   "2026-04-12",
  "season":    2026
}

###

### Open the competition
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/competitions/{{competitionId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "status": "open" }

###

### Create an event (150m Senior Men)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/competitions/{{competitionId}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "distance":    "150m",
  "category":    "senior",
  "gender":      "male",
  "scheduledAt": "2026-04-11T09:00:00"
}

###

### Register a member
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/competitions/{{competitionId}}/events/{{eventId}}/registrations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "memberId": "{{memberId}}" }

###

### Get registrations for event
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/competitions/{{competitionId}}/events/{{eventId}}/registrations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Record a result
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/competitions/{{competitionId}}/events/{{eventId}}/results
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "memberId":       "{{memberId}}",
  "registrationId": "{{registrationId}}",
  "rank":           1,
  "finalTime":      "00:32.4",
  "splitTime500":   "01:48.0",
  "strokeRate":     28,
  "heartRate":      175,
  "watts":          320
}

###

### Get event results (ranked)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/competitions/{{competitionId}}/events/{{eventId}}/results
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}